num = 10**5 * 2 + 1

for i in range(num3):

        ai2[ai[i]] += [[i,1,ai[i]]]
i = num-1
while k > 0:
    for j in ai2[i]:
        if k == 0:
            break
        num2 =  j[2] // (j[1]+1)
        ai2[num2] += [[j[0],j[1]+1,j[2]]]
        print(j[0],end=" ")
